                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The short and sweet answer to this is that we all play the game differently. We each do what is fun for us or we wouldn't play at all. 
<br />

<br />
I do think they made the game to easy in some aspects. Graveyards make CR's in PoP a thing of the past. 
<br />

<br />
Without you having PoP until level 30, you did get to experience some of the old world stuff. The run from Qeynos to Freeport. The taking the boat to different zones. So in reality, you did get to do a lot of those things. The game has changed and SOE has made a lot of things much easier, but it's up to each of us if we use them or not. 
<br />

<br />
I thought your post was a good one though. 
