<a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?p=18979" target="_blank" class="postlink">E63/TT h+ 1.5khp 3.4km ft1 G&lt;3 e+ o++ T+++ L H++ !f g+ b c+++ !t D-- !X</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
