</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>AbitooXev wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Bags.  Every character starts with an 8 slot bag, this is a HUGE advantage because you can start your plat farming at level 1, instead of at whatever level you manage to forage enough to buy your first bag.  ALSO, the increased bank space helps all packrat players who save anything they think might be quest related.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Umm -- I started before this, and got a couple quest boxes...  I don't really see how this helps that much, but OK.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>AbitooXev wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Buffs.  Not counting the middle generation of level 1 KEI babies, buffs especially the cleric HP buff are still super powerful.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
