                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The game is definitely easier than it used to be.  However I'm not sure how big of an effect that's had on players' abilities.  There were incompetent players then; there are incompetent players now.  Advancing in EQ has always been more about how much time you put into it rather than your ability.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal">"Please, someone, teach him how to pronounce nuclear."</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
